      "description": "$19,500 - Fair-condition vehicle with noticeable wear inside and out consistent with age and use. The paint, body, and interior show cosmetic flaws and general wear, but it is still a presentable, usable vehicle. It starts, runs, and drives, though buyers should expect typical age-related imperfections and possible minor repairs or reconditioning.",
