    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition vehicle that shows well and should make a dependable daily driver. It presents nicely overall, with the kind of normal cosmetic wear, small blemishes, and light signs of use you\u2019d expect from a used car, but nothing that takes away from it being a solid, well-kept example. The interior appears well cared for, and the exterior still has good overall presence. If you\u2019re looking for a reliable used vehicle that is better than basic transportation without pretending to be perfect, this is a strong candidate.",
