    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Well-kept classic in good overall condition with solid presentation and the kind of honest, cared-for feel that makes it easy to enjoy right away. It shows nicely, has been clearly looked after, and would make a great driver for someone who wants a clean, attractive example without paying top-tier show-car money.",
