    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical option for buyers seeking low-cost transportation or a project with potential. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values function and value over cosmetics, but it still represents an accessible entry point at a budget-friendly price. A smart choice for the right buyer looking to keep costs down.",
