      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s seen some life, but it still has plenty to offer the right buyer. If you\u2019re after an affordable runabout, a first project, or something to tinker with, this could be a great fit. It\u2019s not perfect and won\u2019t pretend to be, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option with lots of potential for someone handy. Priced to sell and ideal for anyone who values a good deal over showroom looks.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest driver with solid bones and plenty of upside. Starts, runs, and offers a straightforward, mechanical feel that makes it a great candidate for someone who appreciates a simple platform they can sort and enjoy. The chassis feels like a usable foundation, and it has the kind of character you want in a budget-friendly car with room to improve. Not a showpiece, but a worthwhile project, commuter, or weekend fixer for the right buyer. Priced to reflect condition while still offering strong value for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
