      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough for someone who appreciates character over perfection, this car offers an affordable way into dependable daily-driver territory or a rewarding weekend project. It has the kind of well-worn charm that tells stories, with plenty of life left for the right owner who wants practical transportation with personality. If you\u2019ve been searching for an inexpensive ride with potential, this is the kind of opportunity that invites a closer look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
